# CocoMind Tier-1 Build — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

The complete Tier-1 implementation of **CocoMind**, an AI-assisted CRPF Tender Evaluation Platform. 35+ source files across 8 phases.

### Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Ingestion
        A[PDF/DOCX/IMG/ZIP] --> B[Magic-byte Sniffing]
        B --> C[SHA-256 Hash]
        C --> D[Doc-type Heuristic]
    end

    subgraph OCR
        D --> E[Azure Document Intelligence]
        E --> F[Word-level BBox + Confidence]
    end

    subgraph PII Redaction
        F --> G[Presidio + 6 Indian Recognisers]
        G --> H[UUID Reversible Tokens]
    end

    subgraph Retrieval
        H --> I[Spatial Chunker]
        I --> J[BGE-M3 Dense]
        I --> K[Whoosh BM25 Sparse]
        J --> L[RRF Fusion]
        K --> L
    end

    subgraph Extraction
        L --> M[Claude Tool-use]
        M --> N[Normalised Values]
    end

    subgraph Evaluation
        N --> O[Conflict Resolver]
        O --> P["Rule Engine (Pure Python)"]
        P --> Q[VTM Row]
    end

    subgraph Output
        Q --> R[Audit Chain]
        Q --> S[Streamlit Dashboard]
        Q --> T[RTI Export]
    end
```

