## Security Architecture

| Control | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| PII Redaction | Presidio + 6 custom Indian recognisers; UUID tokens; LLM sees only redacted text |
| Rule Engine Isolation | `import-linter` contract enforces zero LLM imports in `src.engine` |
| Audit Integrity | SQLite triggers block UPDATE/DELETE; verify_chain() re-derives all hashes |
| RBAC | 6 personas with least-privilege; denied access is audit-logged |
| Prompt Injection | Rule engine is pure Python — 10 red-team payloads confirmed immune |

