## What Was Tested

| Test Suite | Coverage |
|------------|----------|
| [test_rule_engine.py](file:///d:/Projects/CocoMind/tests/unit/test_rule_engine.py) | All 6 operators, edge cases, date formats, mandatory vs optional |
| Hypothesis property tests | 250+ examples: gte threshold, confidence boundary, none-value invariant |
| [test_audit_chain.py](file:///d:/Projects/CocoMind/tests/unit/test_audit_chain.py) | Write/read, chain integrity, append-only (UPDATE/DELETE blocked), Merkle root, RTI export |
| [test_conflict_resolver.py](file:///d:/Projects/CocoMind/tests/unit/test_conflict_resolver.py) | No conflict, hierarchy resolution, same-rank disagreement → HITL |
| [test_indian_recognizers.py](file:///d:/Projects/CocoMind/tests/unit/test_indian_recognizers.py) | PAN, GSTIN, IFSC, EPFO |
| [test_prompt_injection.py](file:///d:/Projects/CocoMind/tests/red_team/test_prompt_injection.py) | 10 adversarial payloads against rule engine |

