## Next Steps for Tier-2

1. Connect Azure OCR in prod (replace stubs with live API calls)
2. MeriPehchaan OIDC integration (replace header-based auth)
3. DSC (Digital Signature Certificate) via eSign 2.0 API
4. PostgreSQL + Alembic migrations (replace SQLite audit)
5. Deploy Streamlit behind Azure App Service with RBAC proxy
